sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CLI as Orchestrator / Cron
    participant F as Data Fetchers
    participant AI as LLM (OpenRouter)
    participant C as Asset Compiler
    participant S as Slack Sender
    participant L as LinkedIn Browser

    CLI->>F: Execute fetch_reddit_apify.py & fetch_ai_news_rss.py
    F-->>CLI: Save JSON feeds (reddit_data.json, ai_news_data.json)
    
    CLI->>AI: Execute generate_all_content_gemini.py
    AI->>AI: Load JSON feeds & logs
    AI->>AI: Call OpenRouter (Generate texts & JSON metadata)
    AI-->>CLI: Save drafts, carousel_data.json, infographic_data.json
    
    CLI->>AI: Execute correct_posts.py
    AI->>AI: Scan drafts & call OpenRouter for word cleanup
    AI-->>CLI: Overwrite cleaned texts
    
    CLI->>C: Execute build_carousel_today.cjs & cap_infographic_today.cjs
    C->>C: Generate slide HTML templates
    C->>C: Launch Puppeteer Chrome
    C->>C: Screenshot HTML files to PNGs
    C->>C: Merge slide PNGs to PDF (carousel.pdf)
    C-->>CLI: Save PDF and PNG assets
    
    CLI->>S: Execute send_to_slack.py
    S->>S: Read texts, PDF, and PNG
    S->>S: Call Slack Web API (Files & Messages)
    S-->>CLI: Completed successfully
    
    CLI->>L: Execute schedule_all_posts.cjs
    L->>L: Connect Puppeteer to LinkedIn session
    L->>L: Type text, attach PDF/PNG, select date/time slot
    L->>L: Confirm scheduled posts
    L-->>CLI: Pipeline run completed
